<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038535" n="167v"/>
                    <p><lb/>Mitto Tibi inclusam <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs>, quam rogo ut eadem via, qua nuper <rs type="letter">tuam</rs>,
                                        <lb/>eam ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1156417392">Albertum Fridericum Gutt</rs> <subst><del>t</del><add>c</add></subst>rastina die transmittas; inscri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ptionem studio <add><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me</add> omissam, rogo, ut Tu suppleas. Excusa, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, mole<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stiam, qua <add>ego et <rs type="person">amicus</rs> qui <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3169070">Rom<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> est</add>, Te affici<subst><del>o</del><add>mus</add></subst>. Hoc temporis momento accipio <rs type="letter">epi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stolam</rs> Tuam<note type="comment">Dieser Brief wurde verbrannt.</note>, qua me <add>con</add>solari<del> niteris</del> conaris ob sinistrum negotii
                    <lb/>successum, quamque ut jubes protinus comburam. Ad huc autem
                    <lb/>Tibi dico, me omnino tristem <add>simul</add> et iratum esse, et omnino<subst><del>fieri</del><add> me putare quod fiat</add></subst> ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>jor<del>em</del> injuria<del>m</del> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzero</rs> hoc modo, quam si ab ipso <rs type="organisation">Senatu</rs>
                                        <lb/>repudiatus fuisset, <add>quod ut credo non contigisset</add><choice><orig>,</orig><reg>.</reg></choice> Fortassis <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Exc.<hi rend="sup">llmi</hi></abbr> illius <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1111043582">Equit<subst><del>e</del><add>i</add></subst>s</rs><del> minae</del>
                    <lb/><del>tant </del>oppositiones min<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tantum fuerunt<subst><del>,</del><add>.</add></subst> <subst><del>e</del><add>E</add></subst>t si ergo tantopere
                                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimatur <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118607308">Frater <abbr>Joh.</abbr> Jacobus</rs>, cur non vocant illum? Nullum
                    <lb/>mihi simile exemplum narratum fuit, nisi illud quod ante 20<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>
                                        <lb/>annos contigit <subst><del><gap/></del><add>Patri</add></subst> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089410077">Maffei</rs><!-- Im Personenindex aktualisieren. -->, cujus nominatio <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> magistratu facta
                    <lb/>propter propriam ipsius culpam in <rs type="organisation">Senatu</rs> non proposita fuit.
                    <lb/>Sum iratus et<del>p</del> ero porro. Sed sileo.</p> <closer>Tu Vale et mihi fave.
                                        <lb/><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1718-12-16">16. <abbr>Xbris</abbr> 1718</date>. Gaudeat h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c epistola eadem sorte qua prior.</closer>
</div>
